snippet.textDisplay:
Greater population density and more immigration. increasing population results in more people being affected by weather. In the past fewer people were affected by weather events because there were fewer people more people means more epidemics, more weather damage more shortages and higher prices as goods become more scarce owing to increased demand from increase in population.


Weather related emergencies will not be the only danger in situations where the population increase requires more resources on delicate balance between supply and demand. Do not let the symptom of weather change hide the real human emergency on a planet with finite resources. The more of us there is the more we will all be threatened by any change in the environment, including epidemics, fires,inflation,floods,droughts,pollution,food scarcity and food quality.
snippet.textOriginal:
Greater population density and more immigration. increasing population results in more people being affected by weather. In the past fewer people were affected by weather events because there were fewer people  more people means more epidemics, more weather damage more shortages and higher prices as goods become more scarce owing to increased demand from  increase in population.


 Weather related emergencies will not be the only danger in situations where the population increase requires more resources  on delicate balance between supply and demand. Do not let the symptom of weather change hide the real human emergency on a  planet with finite resources. The more of us there is the more we will all be threatened by any change in the environment, including epidemics, fires,inflation,floods,droughts,pollution,food scarcity and food quality.
